  <Placemark>
   <name>Marine Weather Statement issued August 30 at 1:43PM EDT by NWS Miami FL</name>
   <styleUrl>#sev_minor</styleUrl>
   <Style>
    <BalloonStyle />
   </Style>
   <Snippet>The areas affected include...
Biscayne Bay...
Coastal waters from Deerfield Beach to Ocean Reef FL out 20 NM...

At 143 PM EDT, Doppler radar indicated a strong thunderstorm, capable
of producing winds to around 30 knots. This thunderstorm was located
over Biscayne Bay, moving east at 15 knots.</Snippet>
