   <name>Small Craft Advisory issued August 30 at 1:34PM EDT until September 1 at 11:00PM EDT by NWS Jacksonville FL</name>
   <styleUrl>#sev_minor</styleUrl>
   <Style>
    <BalloonStyle />
   </Style>
   <Snippet>* WHAT...Northeast winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 30 kt and
seas 5 to 7 ft expected.

* WHERE...Coastal waters from Altamaha Sound to Fernandina Beach
FL out 20 NM and Waters from Altamaha Sound GA to Fernandina
Beach FL from 20 to 60 NM.

* WHEN...From 11 AM Sunday to 11 PM EDT Monday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.</Snippet>
