   </Style>
   <Snippet>* WHAT...Minor flooding is occurring and minor flooding is forecast.

* WHERE...Savannah River near Clyo.

* WHEN...Until Monday morning.

* IMPACTS...At 11.0 feet, the back yards of several homes on Tom
Goethe Road flood.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...
- At 915 AM EDT Saturday, the stage was 11.6 feet.
- Forecast...The river is expected to fall below flood stage
Sunday evening and continue falling to 9.7 feet Thursday
morning.
- Flood stage is 11.0 feet.</Snippet>
