   <Style>
    <BalloonStyle />
   </Style>
   <Snippet>* WHAT...Northwest winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 35 kt and
combined seas 6 to 8 ft expected when conditions are worst.

* WHERE...Point Piedras Blancas to Point Sal from 10 to 60 NM.

* WHEN...For the Small Craft Advisory, until 5 PM PDT this
afternoon. For the Gale Warning, from 5 PM this afternoon to 3
